RESTRICTIONS

You are NOT permitted to:

1. SELL OR REDISTRIBUTE THE GAME — You may not sell, redistribute, or publish
   any product that substantially reproduces The Game's content, experience, or
   identity, whether using The Codebase, Non-Code Assets, or both.

2. MONETIZE USING NON-CODE ASSETS — You may not monetize any project that
   incorporates Non-Code Assets from The Game in any form, including but not
   limited to: selling the project, accepting donations tied to the project,
   placing it behind a paywall, or running advertisements on or within it.

3. RELEASE FULL GAME PORTS — You may not publish a full or substantially
   complete playable port of The Game to another language, platform, or engine,
   regardless of whether Non-Code Assets are included.

4. OMIT CREDIT — Any publicly released Derivative Work, mod, patch, or port
   must clearly credit Cotordo Games (DJ / Djalroid) as the original author of
   The Codebase. Failure to provide visible, reasonable credit constitutes a
   violation of this license.

5. SUBLICENSE — You may not relicense The Codebase or any Derivative Work
   under different terms that would grant permissions beyond those defined here.

6. CLAIM OWNERSHIP — You may not represent The Codebase, The Game, or any
   substantial portion thereof as your own original work.

